latestIgtvVideos.title: Farida Gupta X Medha Bahuguna
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
My journey with @faridagupta dates back to almost 5 years now and this label is just so special to me. I did my VERY FIRST independent shoot while I was still in college for their first campaign and I still remember the thrill and excitement I had to work for them :’)

FG is known for their beautiful block prints, Jaipur cotton and classic Indian silhouettes that makes you feel at ease round the clock.

Here I am feeling even more comfortable in their newly launched collection “Roza” that makes you instantly ready to lounge your time away ! 😍

Conceptualised, directed, shot, styled and edited by me. 

This beautiful song : Mai ni meriye 
@loststoriesmusic @jonitamusic @ashwinadwani @artist.originals
